===Format===
* '''Semi finals''' : ''June 22th - 24th
** 24 Invited Teams.
** 5 Matches Per day.
** Teams are divided equally in 3 groups of 8.
** Round-robin format.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 14 teams}} qualify for ''finals.
** {{bgcolortext|up|2 Fan Favourite}} teams will qualify to ''finals.
{{VerticalMargin}}
* '''Finals''' : ''June 27th - July 1st
** 16 teams , 5 matchdays.
** 20 matches (4 each day).
{{VerticalMargin}}
